Package: grizbayr
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Inference for A|B and Bandit Marketing Tests
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ryan Angi
Maintainer: Ryan Angi <rangi@redventures.com>
Description: Uses simple Bayesian conjugate prior update rules to calculate 
    the following metrics for various marketing objectives: Win Probability 
    of each option, Value Remaining in the Test, and Percent Lift Over the 
    Baseline.
